PREFACE.

DR. TISCHER’S edition of the Tusculan Disputations is included in Haupt and Sauppe's “ Collection of Greek and Roman Authors with German Notes.²’ It will be found a very useful edition, tho remarks being clearly and accurately expressed, and the amount of them very judiciously proportioned to the

real wants of the student. T. Κ. A.

June 6, 1851.
